<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Panel de Administración - Sistema Hospitalario</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        /* Estilos específicos para el Dashboard que complementan al styles.css */
        .dashboard-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #334e68;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }
        .card:hover {
            border-color: #1992d4;
            background: #f0f9ff;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        .card-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            display: block;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="login-container" style="max-width: 700px;">
        <h2>Hospital Central</h2>
        <h3>Panel de Control - Personal Administrativo</h3>
        
        <p style="text-align: left;">Bienvenido al sistema. Seleccione la acción que desea realizar:</p>

        <div class="dashboard-grid">
            <a href="/pacientes/registrar" class="card">
                <span class="card-icon">👤</span>
                Registrar Paciente (RF-01)
            </a>

        <a href="/turnos/asignar" class="card">
            <span class="card-icon">📅</span>
            Asignar Turno (RF-08)
        </a>

            <a href="#" class="card" style="opacity: 0.6; cursor: not-allowed;">
                <span class="card-icon">🔍</span>
                Consultar Turnos (RF-25)
            </a>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 2.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; text-align: right;">
            <a href="/auth/login" style="color: #b82525; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Cerrar Sesión →</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>